name: Take Me Home (itch) (Jettersfreak)
description:
Home is where the heart is, but right now, this cat has lost its way. It may be far from where it needs to be, but with every puzzle, it gets closer and closer.

(I'm so tired I'm on 2 hours of sleep and our real cat actually ran away during the jam, (but we found her a couple of hours later) so please enjoy what we managed to frantically scrapped together in the few hours we had left!)
